    <sect3 role="package">
      <title>Introduo a Gi-DocGen Module</title>

      <para>
        <application>Gi-DocGen</application> is a document generator for
GObject-based libraries. GObject is the base type system of the GNOME
project. GI-Docgen reuses the introspection data generated by GObject-based
libraries to generate the API reference of these libraries, as well as other
ancillary documentation.
      </para>

      &lfs113_checked;

